Description: ## Thermos CLI
        
        A flask command line interface built on python. 
        
        ## Note
        
        If you wish to collaborate,visit: https://github.com/zecollokaris/Thermos-cli OR  https://github.com/mwangi-njuguna/thermos-cli
        
        
        ## Prerequisites
        
        Both the CLI and generated project have dependencies that require python3.6.
        
        ## Table of Contents
        
